def v1 := 100000000000 + 100000000000
def v2 := 200000000000
def v3 := 200000000001

def v5 := 100000000000 - 100000000000
def c1 := reduceNat v1

def c3 := reduceNat v3
def c4 := reduceBool v4
def c5 := reduceNat v5

#eval checkDefEq `c1 `c3
#guard_msgs in
#eval checkDefEq `Nat.zero `c5
